    <p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl font-body text-lg leading-9 text-white/50 md:text-xl">
      Syncing human circadian rhythms with the forest's natural cycles. Lighting, air quality, and acoustic balance optimized for well-being.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 w-full">
      <div class="liquid-panel rounded-[2rem] p-8">
        <div class="font-sans text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-white/40">Well-being Score</div>
        <div class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold">98/100</div>
      </div>
      <div class="liquid-panel rounded-[2rem] p-8">
        <div class="font-sans text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-white/40">Oxygen Saturation</div>
        <div class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold">+12%</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
